              "answer": "\u25cf Close any wound leaks\n\u25cf Topical corticosteroids, cycloplegics\n\u25cf If severe hypotony with lens/IOL \u2013 cornea touch, flat A/C \u2013 reform A/C at slit lamp with BSS or viscoelastic.\n\u25cf Surgical drainage via sclerotomies for flat or progressively shallow AC, particularly in the presence of inflammation,\ncorneal decompensation from lens-cornea touch, \u201ckissing\u201d choroidals",
              "keyPoints": [
                "Close any wound leaks",
                "Topical corticosteroids, cycloplegics",
                "If severe hypotony with lens/IOL \u2013 cornea touch, flat A/C \u2013 reform A/C at slit lamp with BSS or viscoelastic.",
