          "questions": [
            {
              "number": 1,
              "question": "Discussion",
              "answer": "From bag to sulcus\n\u25aa 17-26D minus 1.0 D\n\u25aa Long eye (>26), minus 1.5D\n\u25aa Short eye (<17) minus 0.5D\nFrom bag to AC\n\u25aa 17-26D minus 1.5 D\n\u25aa Long eye (>26), minus 2.0D\n\u25aa Short eye (<17), minus 1.0D\nThis is only a general guide and you should always have the patient\u2019s IOL calculations in the OR.",
              "keyPoints": [
                "17-26D minus 1.0 D",
